  "text": "In contrast to these data, an inferior accuracy for USCOM was reported by other authors who found that CO measurements by USCOM do not reliably represent absolute values as compared to pulmonary artery catheter thermodilution technique [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Possible explanations for such incoherent findings are as follows.",
